# Liquid Glass Design

- App chrome uses `GlassPanel` (`backdrop-blur-xl`, `border-white/20`, orange mesh behind).
- Primary actions use `--primary` orange CSS tokens, not arbitrary hex colors.
- Contract editor/preview **body** is solid white paper — no glass or mesh inside the document.
- Max 3–4 glass surfaces per screen; use `rounded-2xl`+ and `transition-all duration-300` on interactive glass.
- PDF/print styles exclude blur and transparency.
